26:34.059 --> 26:40.132 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But first: Torrential rains and
flooding in
Southern and Central Texas have
made for a

26:40.165 --> 26:42.601 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
