evacuated. At least
six people have died since last
week. And

26:58.116 --> 27:02.387 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
more rain is expected in the
coming days as
the weather pattern pushes east.

27:02.421 --> 27:05.123 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We get a report from one of the
worst-hit
areas.

27:05.157 --> 27:10.162 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Jeff Braun is the emergency
management coordinator
in Fort Bend County and joins me
via Skype.

27:10.195 --> 27:14.333 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
