27:16.168 --> 27:19.271 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFF BRAUN, Emergency Management
Coordinator,
Fort Bend County: No. No, Hari,
we have not

27:19.304 --> 27:24.276 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
