the county,
and there's a gauge there that
everybody bases

27:28.580 --> 27:30.582 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
their flood finding on.

27:30.616 --> 27:37.756 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The record was 50.3 at that
gauge. We're going
to be somewhere about four feet
or a little

27:37.789 --> 27:43.629 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
