the Gulf of
Mexico, which then results in
flooding.

31:23.849 --> 31:27.652 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We have done a lot of work
locally to help
mitigate against the flooding.
There is still

31:27.686 --> 31:32.290 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
