city and our
partners at Harris County, Fort
Bend County,

31:32.324 --> 31:37.696 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Montgomery County, all the
different jurisdictions
around us, we are really
committed to helping

31:37.729 --> 31:41.967 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to solve some of these flooding
problems,
and also just letting people
know what to

31:42.000 --> 31:46.605 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
expect and what steps they need
to take to
prepare ahead of these types of
situations.

31:46.638 --> 31:50.475 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Flooding is
one of those
things that you can somewhat
prepare for when

31:50.509 --> 31:54.146 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
