and small essays.

44:08.379 --> 44:13.017 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I think it was important for
me to get
the entire story down. It was
submitted originally

44:13.050 --> 44:17.855 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
just about Iraq. And at that
point, editors
and agents suggested that I
needed to spend

44:17.889 --> 44:19.657 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
