of war camps.

48:41.118 --> 48:47.124 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Did you come away
of a clear
idea of what is within the
bounds of what

48:47.158 --> 48:54.799 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
