interrogating someone
who has done something terrible
against the

48:54.832 --> 49:00.004 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
United States, whether it's ISIS
or al-Qaida
or something, and what steps
over the line?

49:00.037 --> 49:02.139 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Did you come away knowing what
that line is?

49:02.173 --> 49:03.908 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
ERIC FAIR: No.

49:03.941 --> 49:06.343 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I think that's an excellent
question,
because I think once you begin
to push the

49:06.377 --> 49:10.481 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
