49:54.291 --> 49:57.661 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We care about what we're doing.
We care about
the image that we project. We
have an obligation

49:57.695 --> 50:02.499 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to things like the Constitution
and the Bill
of Rights. And those things
require us to

50:02.533 --> 50:03.868 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
behave in a certain way.

50:03.901 --> 50:07.471 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Eric Fair, the
